intro:
Study about political policies

Thank you for taking part in this survey!



In the survey, we will show you political information, and we will ask you questions about the information you received, your background, and your opinions on various topics. 



You can be sure that all your answers will remain anonymous. It is impossible to attribute answers to a specific person, and we are legally obliged to protect the anonymity of all participants.



It takes about 5 minutes to complete the survey.



This survey is conducted by researchers at the University of MÃ¼nster.

If you have any questions or comments, please feel free to contact us.



Dr Mirko Wegemann, m.wegemann@uni-muenster.de
